This workshop is aimed at enlightening business users and people regarding the principles of Agile and Scrum.  By applying these principles within their working environments, it is our belief that they will better understand their interactions with their developers, and also implement these effective techniques in their own work towards becoming more effective at delivering value within their corporate environment.
